name: Symbol Meta Map, The Era of Queen of the Abyss
description:
These are a few of the most common symbols.
All symbols have variations depending on the frequency of the gargle and the time period context.

The symbols, or emblems, are often made by the cult members themselves during obscure torture and severe lack of oxygen. There is no indication that these symbols have any other function than to facilitate the transmission of thoughts during silent rituals and as a frequency indicator during gargling. However, there are older writings that emphasize the function of the symbols as keys. In fact, in some of these very difficult-to-interpret writings, the symbols are not referred to as symbols but as keys.
